      <title>韩国医生因争夺医学院席位而大规模罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/south-korean-doctors-set-for-mass-walkout-over-med-school-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最大的医生游说团体周二举行了为期一天的全国性罢工，进一步加剧了为期四个月的抗议政府增加医学院招生数量决定的劳工行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/south-korean-doctors-set-for-mass-walkout-over-med-school-seats</guid>
